 />\n<br />\n但可以講既係西方樂理都係以古典音樂為起源，流行曲d chord progression 都係黎自古典"},{"pid":"90e36f1880597a4ec16aad31f96340ee75ed4991","tid":1910652,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T08:54:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">紐約大都會歌劇院 (The Metropolitan Opera)因疫情關閉，從3月16日至22日，美國東岸時間每晚7:30，每晚上載一部該劇院Live in HD系列的作品，免費上載播放。上載後20個小時內有效。<br />\nMonday, March 16 &ndash; Bizet&rsquo;s Carmen<br />\n<br />\nTuesday, March 17 &ndash; Puccini&rsquo;s La Boh&egrave;me<br />\n<br />\nWednesday, March 18 &ndash; Verdi&rsquo;s Il Trovatore<br />\n<br />\nThursday, March 19 &ndash; Verdi&rsquo;s La Traviata<br />\n<br />\nFriday, March 20 &ndash; Donizetti&rsquo;s La Fille du R&eacute;giment<br />\n<br />\nSaturday, March 21 &ndash; Donizetti&rsquo;s Lucia di Lammermoor<br />\n<br />\nSunday, March 22 &ndash; Tchaikovsky&rsquo;s Eugene Onegin<br />\n</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.metopera.org/about/press-releases/met-to-launch-nightly-met-opera-streams-a-free-series-of-encore-live-in-hd-presentations-streamed-on-the-company-website-during-the-coronavirus-closure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.metopera.org%2Fabout%2Fpress-releases%2Fmet-to-launch-nightly-met-opera-streams-a-free-series-of-encore-live-in-hd-presentations-streamed-on-the-company-website-during-the-coronavirus-closure%2F&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbICcuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=6ea02da4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.metopera.org/about/press-releases/met-to-launch-nightly-met-opera-streams-a-free-series-of-encore-live-in-hd-presentations-streamed-on-the-company-website-during-the-coronavirus-closure/</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">柏林愛樂廳（The Philharmonie Berlin）也要閉館 ,將網上音樂庫免費開放30日。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.berliner-philharmoniker.de/en/titelgeschichten/20192020/digital-concert-hall/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.berliner-philharmoniker.de%2Fen%2Ftitelgeschichten%2F20192020%2Fdigital-concert-hall%2F&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbICcuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=c65d8420\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.berliner-philharmoniker.de/en/titelgeschichten/20192020/digital-concert-hall/</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">罕有 - 香港話劇團一連五個星期六8點，免費播放 戲寶重溫</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/125415688981/posts/10158452477333982/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F125415688981%2Fposts%2F10158452477333982%2F&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbICcuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=4f82a97c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/125415688981/posts/10158452477333982/</a>"}]}